## Interface (TFT, 160×80 Landscape)

### Main screen (Idle)

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│USB                             [3/5]  Ready        │
│WiFiGrab                                            │
└────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

| Position | Content | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| Top‑left | `USB` or `BLE` | Mode indicator. USB = cyan. BLE = green (connected) / red (disconnected). |
| Top‑right | `[3/5]` | Current script number / total scripts. |
| Top‑right (after counter) | `Ready` | Status text. Other values: `Run?`, `Run…`, `Done!`, `Err`, `Wait pair` (BLE). |
| Middle | `WiFiGrab` | Script filename (without `.txt`), truncated to ~12 chars, larger font. |

### Mode selection menu (long press Center)

```
Select HID Mode:
  USB   BLE
Up/Down  Center
```

- Highlight moves with Up/Down.
- Short Center confirms.

### No scripts found

```
No scripts
```

### Error messages

- `LittleFS mount failed!`  
- `No BLE conn`  
- `Can't open file`  
- `Invalid script`

Errors appear briefly (2s) then return to main screen or sleep.

