## Summary of User Interactions

| Action | Result |
|--------|--------|
| Up / Down | Switch to previous/next script |
| Short press Center | Enter confirm mode (status `Run?`) |
| Short press Center again (within 2s) | Execute current script |
| Up / Down during confirm | Cancel execution |
| Long press Center (1s) | Enter mode selection menu |
| In menu: Up/Down | Toggle USB / BLE |
| In menu: Short Center | Confirm selection (reboot if changed) |
| No activity for 2 minutes | Deep sleep (if conditions met) |
| Any button press (while sleeping) | Wake up (reboot) |

